sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router / LB<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Envoy as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KAP as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-CA)
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth /<br/>OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Service<br/>(via HTTPRoute)
    participant Admin as Admin / User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DSCICtrl as DSCI Controller
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controller
    participant GWCtrl as Gateway Controller

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Upstream: Flow 1: User Authentication via Gateway (RHOAI 3.x)
        User->>Router: HTTPS Request (no auth)
        Router->>Envoy: Forward (TLS terminate/reencrypt)
        Envoy->>KAP: ext_authz check<br/>Cookie / None
        KAP->>OAuth: OAuth2/OIDC<br/>Client Credentials
        OAuth-->>KAP: Token Response
        KAP-->>Envoy: Auth Result + Token
        Envoy->>Upstream: Forward (Lua filter strips cookies)<br/>Bearer Token (x-forwarded-access-token)
        Upstream-->>Envoy: Response
        Envoy-->>Router: Response
        Router-->>User: HTTPS Response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Admin,CompCtrl: Flow 2: Component Provisioning
        Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification
        DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create component CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>CompCtrl: Watch notification
        CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply kustomize manifests<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>CompCtrl: Resources created
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Admin,GWCtrl: Flow 3: Platform Initialization
        Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>DSCICtrl: Watch notification
        DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create namespace, ConfigMaps<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Auth CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create GatewayConfig CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>GWCtrl: Watch notification
        GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Gateway, EnvoyFilter,<br/>kube-auth-proxy<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    end
